'''Taẓuṛi tamaziɣt''' tga yan iger bahra istawhmman g Tmazɣa.

==Ssinima==
<blockquote>''Ɣr uggar f [[Ssinima tamaziɣt]]''</blockquote>'''Ssinima tamaziɣt''' tga tt ssinima lli ittuysawaln s [[tutlayin timaziɣin]], tbda ɣ ugafa n tfriqt ɣ tmazirt n [[Lmɣrib]] ɣ lbdya n 90's ɣ tasut tis 20, ɛad ad tbayn ɣ tmazirt n [[Dzayr]] ɣ uzmz ad nit. Tkka-tt-inn tuddma nɣ lbidaya n ssinima tamaziɣt ɣ tmazirt n [[Sus]] ɣ usggwas n 1991 ɣ [[Lmɣrib]] s lfilm lli akk izwarn n tutlayt [[taclḥit]] ad tt igan " [[Tamɣart n Wurɣ|''Tamɣart n Wurɣ'']] " lli d issufɣ ssi [[Ḥasan Bizikarn]], d awsn gis kigan n inaẓurn imaziɣn. Isawl d ifilm ad f kigan n tɣawsiwin gisn tamagit d wakal d waddur. Iḍfart nit ɣ usggwas n 1992 film lli akk ittawssan ɣ ssinima [[taclḥit]] d [[Tutlayin timaziɣin|tamaziɣt]], ad t igan lfilm n " [[Butfunast|''Bu-tfunast'']] " lli d isnkrn yat tgrawla imqqurn ɣ ssinima tamaziɣt s umyawas n ssi [[Muḥammad Baɛmran]] d ssi [[Ḥasan Ibuka]]. Iḍfart ula ntta lfilm n " [[Gar Timɣarin|''Gar Timɣarin'']] ", ɛad ad ackin kigan n laflam yaḍni.

